 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; flex:2.0375;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 49.079754601226995%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Russian landscape\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/3fcaa4049628c84772407c638ec88857/a6d36/imperial-russia-feature.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/3fcaa4049628c84772407c638ec88857/222b7/imperial-russia-feature.png 163w,\n/static/3fcaa4049628c84772407c638ec88857/ff46a/imperial-russia-feature.png 325w,\n/static/3fcaa4049628c84772407c638ec88857/a6d36/imperial-russia-feature.png 650w,\n/static/3fcaa4049628c84772407c638ec88857/e548f/imperial-russia-feature.png 975w,\n/static/3fcaa4049628c84772407c638ec88857/3c492/imperial-russia-feature.png 1300w,\n/static/3fcaa4049628c84772407c638ec88857/29114/imperial-russia-feature.png 1920w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>If you are reading a literary book about 18th century, or studying history, or you feel limited with the standard units of measurements, or by any other means find yourself curious about historic units used one or two centuries ago, like when it was time of Russian Empire, then this app might take you interest.</p>\n<p>Jump into the new world measured by arshin, versta, sazhen. Measure like Russian.</p>\n<p>This app includes simple arithmetic calculator.</p>\n<p>Stay tuned for the updates. More features are coming soon.</p>\n<p><a href=\"/projects/imperial-russia/privacy-policy\">Privacy Policy</a></p>","excerpt":"Opened beta testing! Hurrah! Google Play and the Google Play logo are trademarks of Google LLC. Short Description Imperial Russia - Historic…","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#short-description\">Short Description</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#full-description\">Full description</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"date":"March 26, 2020","published":"March 27, 2020","lastModified":"October 13, 2021","title":"Imperial Russia: Historic unit converter","subtitle":null,"section":null,"draft":null,"developing":null,"buttonText":null,"buttonLink":null,"secondButtonText":null,"secondButtonLink":null,"featuredImage":{"publicURL":"/static/ed6b2110dddc852514ca1ce00a38c442/imperial-russia-screen.png","childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"fullWidth","backgroundColor":"#d8d8e8","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/ed6b2110dddc852514ca1ce00a38c442/25dbe/imperial-russia-screen.png","srcSet":"/static/ed6b2110dddc852514ca1ce00a38c442/fd347/imperial-russia-screen.png 576w,\n/static/ed6b2110dddc852514ca1ce00a38c442/a0f02/imperial-russia-screen.png 768w,\n/static/ed6b2110dddc852514ca1ce00a38c442/25dbe/imperial-russia-screen.png 922w","sizes":"100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/ed6b2110dddc852514ca1ce00a38c442/ad4e4/imperial-russia-screen.webp 576w,\n/static/ed6b2110dddc852514ca1ce00a38c442/1171c/imperial-russia-screen.webp 768w,\n/static/ed6b2110dddc852514ca1ce00a38c442/5663c/imperial-russia-screen.webp 922w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"100vw"}]},"width":1,"height":0.6247288503253796}}}}}},"pageContext":{"showLikes":true,"absolutePath":"/home/runner/work/mikolasan.github.io/mikolasan.github.io/src/markdown/projects/imperial-russia.md","url":"/projects/imperial-russia","next":{"excerpt":"One app per month - mastering Code and Self The Concept The idea is simple yet profound – dedi